sequenceDiagram
  participant Device
  participant Tower
  participant LawN as Law-N Node
  participant CLSI
  participant Cloud

  Device->>Tower: Emit signal + LSIP identity
  Tower->>LawN: Forward signal metadata
  LawN->>CLSI: Expose state (routes, patterns)
  CLSI->>Cloud: Schedule workload close to Device
  Cloud->>Device: Response via optimized route
